    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# User Feedback Theme Mining\\n\",\"**NLP Project 78 of 100** — Cluster app-store or survey comments into themes using TF-IDF + K-Means.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.cluster import KMeans\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"feedback = [\\n    'App crashes frequently on Android','Keeps crashing when I open photos','Force close every time',\\n    'Love the new dark mode feature','Dark mode is beautiful','Finally added dark theme',\\n    'Loading time is way too slow','Takes forever to load','Performance is sluggish',\\n    'Battery drain is terrible','Uses too much battery','Drains battery in 2 hours',\\n    'UI redesign looks amazing','New interface is clean','Love the updated design',\\n] * 10\\ndf = pd.DataFrame({'feedback': feedback})\\ndf = df.sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\n\\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=2000, stop_words='english')\\nX = tfidf.fit_transform(df['feedback'])\\nkm = KMeans(n_clusters=5, random_state=SEED, n_init=10)\\ndf['theme'] = km.fit_predict(X)\\n\\nterms = tfidf.get_feature_names_out()\\nprint('Discovered Themes:')\\nfor i in range(5):\\n    top = [terms[j] for j in km.cluster_centers_[i].argsort()[-4:][::-1]]\\n    count = (df['theme']==i).sum()\\n    print(f'  Theme {i} ({count} items): {top}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"df['theme'].value_counts().sort_index().plot(kind='bar', color='steelblue', title='Feedback Themes')\\nplt.xlabel('Theme'); plt.ylabel('Count'); plt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Unsupervised theme mining reveals common feedback categories.**\\n\",\"- **Top terms per cluster provide interpretable labels.**\\n\",\"- **For production, track theme volumes over app versions.**\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
